\c 17
\s Imithetho yokuhlaba
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Tshono kuAroni lakumadodana akhe, lebantwaneni bonke bakoIsrayeli, uthi kubo: Leli yilizwi iN\nd kosi\nd* elaye ngalo isithi:
\v 3 Loba ngubani wendlu kaIsrayeli ohlaba inkabi\x + Dute. 12.5,6,13,14,15,21.\x* loba imvu loba imbuzi enkambeni, kumbe ekuhlabela ngaphandle kwenkamba,
\v 4 engakulethanga emnyango wethente lenhlangano ukunikela umnikelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni phambi kwethabhanekele leN\nd kosi\nd*, igazi lizabalelwa lowomuntu, uchithile igazi; ngakho lowomuntu uzaqunywa asuke ebantwini bakibo\x + 16.9,10. Eks. 30.33.\x*.
\v 5 Ukuze, lapho abantwana bakoIsrayeli beletha imihlatshelo yabo, abayihlabela endle\x + 14.7.\x*, bayilethe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni emnyango wethente lenhlangano, kumpristi, bayihlabe ibe yimihlatshelo yeminikelo yokuthula eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 3.2.\x*.
\v 6 Njalo umpristi uzafafaza igazi phezu kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 3.2.\x* emnyango wethente lenhlangano, atshise amahwahwa, abe luqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Gen. 8.21; Levi 4.31.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo kabasayikuhlabela amadimoni\x + 2 Lan. 11.15.\x* imihlatshelo yabo, ababephinga ngokuwalandela\x + Eks. 34.15.\x*. Lokhu kuzakuba yisimiso esilaphakade kubo ezizukulwaneni zabo.
\p
\v 8 Tshono-ke kubo \add uthi\add*: Ngulowo lalowo wendlu kaIsrayeli, lakowemzini ohlala njengowezizwe phakathi kwabo, onikela umnikelo wokutshiswa loba umhlatshelo\x + 1.2,3.\x*,
\v 9 angawulethi emnyango wethente lenhlangano ukuze awenzele iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 17.4.\x*, lowomuntu uzaqunywa asuke ebantwini bakibo.
\s Igazi kalivunyelwa ukudliwa
\p
\v 10 Njalo ngulowo lalowo wendlu kaIsrayeli, lakowemzini ohlala njengowezizwe phakathi kwabo, odla loba yiliphi igazi\x + 3.17.\x*, ngizamisa ubuso bami bumelane lomphefumulo odla igazi\x + 20.3,6; 26.17; Hez. 14.8. 15.7.\x*, ngiwuqume usuke phakathi kwabantu bawo.
\v 11 Ngoba impilo yenyama isegazini\x + 17.14.\x*; mina-ke ngilinike lona phezu kwelathi ukwenzela imiphefumulo yenu inhlawulo yokuthula\x + Mat. 26.28. Mark. 14.24. Roma 3.25. 5.9. Efe. 1.7. Kol. 1.14,20. Heb. 13.12. 1 Joha. 1.7. Isam. 1.5.\x*; ngoba kuligazi elenzela umphefumulo inhlawulo yokuthula\x + Heb. 9.22.\x*.
\v 12 Ngakho ngathi ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli: Kakungabi lamphefumulo kini odla igazi; lowemzini ohlala njengowezizwe phakathi kwenu kangadli igazi.
\v 13 Njalo ngulowo lalowo ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli, lakowemzini ohlala njengowezizwe phakathi kwabo, ozingela inyama yenyamazana kumbe inyoni edliwayo, uzathulula igazi layo\x + Dute. 12.16,24. 15.23.\x*, aligqibele ngenhlabathi\x + Hez. 24.7.\x*.
\v 14 Ngoba kuyimpilo yenyama yonke\x + 17.11. Gen. 9.4.\x*; igazi layo lisempilweni yayo; yikho ngathi ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli: Lingadli igazi loba ngelayiphi inyama, ngoba impilo yayo yonke inyama kuligazi layo; loba ngubani olidlayo uzaqunywa.
\v 15 Futhi wonke umphefumulo odla ingcuba\x + Eks. 22.31. Levi 7.24. 11.40. 22.8. Dute. 14.21. Hez. 4.14. 44.31.\x* kumbe inyamazana edatshuliweyo phakathi\x + Gen. 31.39.\x* kwabokuzalwa elizweni kumbe phakathi kwabemzini\x + 16.29. 18.26. 19.34.\x*, uzahlamba izembatho zakhe\x + 11.25.\x*, ageze ngamanzi\x + 15.5.\x*, abe ngongcolileyo kuze kuhlwe; emva kwalokho uzahlambuluka.
\v 16 Kodwa uba enga\add zi\add*watshi, engagezi umzimba wakhe, uzathwala ububi bakhe\x + 5.1. Nani 19.20.\x*.